<plot>However strong their faith, life hasn't been easy on Leon and Margot de Ruyter, a young, strongly religious couple. God hasn't answered their prayers for a healthy child and it seems like the difficult birth they're coping with now, will end in yet another tragedy. Little do Leon and Margot realize, however, that an even darker shadow looms above. Something that will change their lives, and the lives of an entire city, forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?131392</url></doc>
